Package: Rmoji
Type: Package
Title: Insert Emojis in R Scripts and Documents
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Berhe Tesfay [aut, cre] (<berhe.etsay@gmail.com>)
Maintainer: Berhe Tesfay <berhe.etsay@gmail.com>
Description: Provides functions and RStudio add-ins to insert emojis directly into 
    R scripts, R Markdown, and Quarto documents. Includes shortcut support, a master 
    emoji list, and Git commit emoji helpers.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.4)
Imports:
    rstudioapi,
    shiny
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
URL: https://github.com/3p1d3m/Rmoji
